\c 5
\s Mufananidzo wemunda wemizambiringa
\p
\v 1 Rega ndiimbire mudiwa wangu rwiyo rwemudiwa wangu pamusoro pemunda wake wemizambiringa. Mudiwa wangu waiva nemunda wemizambiringa pachikomo chakaorera.
\v 2 Zvino wakaushosha, ndokubudisa matombo awo, ndokuusima mizambiringa yakaisvonaka, ndokuvaka shongwe mukati mawo, ndokucherawo chisviniro mukati mawo; zvino akatarira kuti uchabereke mazambiringa, asi wakabereka mazambiringa emusango.
\v 3 Zvino ikozvino vagari veJerusarema, nevarume vaJudha, tongai henyu pakati pangu nemunda wangu wemizambiringa.
\v 4 Kungadai kwakaitirweizve munda wemizambiringa, chandisina kuita mauri! Naizvozvo ndakamirira kuti uchabereka mazambiringa, asi wakabereka mazambiringa emusango?
\v 5 Zvino regai ndikuzivisei zvandichaitira munda wangu wemizambiringa: Ndichabvisa ruzhowa rwawo, kuti uve ufuro, kuputsa rusvingo rwawo, ugova nzvimbo yekutsikwa tsikwa.
\v 6 Zvino ndichauita chakaparadzwa, haungachekererwi kana kutimbirirwa, asi uchamera minzwa neukato, Ndicharairawo makore kuti asanaisa mvura pamusoro pawo.
\v 7 Nokuti munda wemizambiringa waJehovha wehondo iimba yaIsraeri, varume vaJudha muti wake unofadza. Zvino wakamirira mutongo \add wakarurama\add*, asi tarira, kuparadzwa kwerop, kururama, asi tarira, kuchema.
\p
\v 8 Nhamo kune vanobatanidza imba neimba, munda nemunda vachiswededzanisa, kusvika pasina nzvimbo, uye imwi mogara muri mega pakati penyika.
\v 9 Munzeve dzangu Jehovha wehondo \add wakati\add*: Zvirokwazvo, dzimba zhinji dzichava matongo, huru nedzakanaka dziripi nhasi.
\v 10 Nokuti maeka gumi emiinda yemizambiringa achabereka bati rimwe chete, nehomeri rembeu richabereka efa.
\p
\v 11 Vane nhamo vanomuka mangwanani, vachidzingana nezvinwiwa zvinodhaka, vanorivara kusvika kwavira, waini yavapfutidza.
\v 12 Rudimbwa, nembira, nengoma, nenyere, newaini zvaiva pamitambo yavo; asi havana kurangarira basa raJehovha kana kuva nehanya nebasa remaoko ake.
\p
\v 13 Naizvozvo vanhu vangu vachaenda muutapwa nekuda kwekusava neruzivo, nevarume vavo vanokudzwa vane nzara, uye ruzhinji rwavo rwuchaomerwa nenyota.
\v 14 Naizvozvo Sheori rakazvitatamura nekushamisa muromo waro zvisina chyero; kusvika kwaburuka rukudzo rwavo nekuwanda kwavo, newanofara pakati pavo.
\v 15 Newakaderera achakotamisirwa pasi, newakakwirira achaninipiswa, uye meso eanozvikudza achaderedzwa.
\v 16 Asi Jehovha wehondo achakwiridzwa pamutongo, naMwari mutsvene achanatswa mukururama.
\v 17 Zvino makwayana achafura senzira yawo, uye vaenzi vachadya matongo evakakora.
\v 18 Nhamo kune kune vanokweva chitadzo nerwodzi rwusina maturo, nechivi sebote rengoro!
\v 19 vanoti: Ngaakurumidze, ngaachimbidzikise basa rake, kuti tione; nezano reMutsvene waIsraeri ngariswedere riuye, kuti tizive.
\p
\v 20 Nhamo kune vanoti kune chakaipa chakanaka; vachiisa rima pachinzvimbo chechiedza, nechiedza pachinzvimbo cherima; vachiisa zvinovava pachinzvimbo chezvinotapira, nezvinotapira pachinzvimbo chezvinovava.
\v 21 Nhamo kune vakachenjera pameso avo, nevanonzwisisa pamberi pechiso chavo.
\v 22 Nhamo kumagamba ekunwa waini, nevarume vane simba rekusanganisa zvinwiwa zvinodhaka;
\v 23 vanoti wakaipa haana mhosva nekuda kwefufuro, vachibvisa kururama kwevakarurama kubva kwavari.
\v 24 Naizvozvo murazvo wemoto sezvaunopedza hundi uye uswa hwakawoma huchiperera mumurazvo, \add saizvozvo\add* mudzi wavo uchava sekuora, neruva ravo richapepereka seguruva; nokuti vakaramba murairo waJehovha wehondo, nekushora shoko reMutsvene waIsraeri.
\v 25 Naizvozvo kutsamwa kwaJehovha kwakapfutira vanhu vake, akatandavadza ruoko rwake kuvarwisa, akavarova; makomo anodedera, mitumbi yavo yafanana namarara pakati penzira dzomumusha. Kunyange zvakadaro, kutsamwa kwake hakuna kudzorwa, asi ruoko rwake rwakaramba rwakatandavadzwa nazvino.
\p
\v 26 Achasimudzira marudzi anobva kure mureza, nokuvaridzira muridzo ivo vari kumigumo yenyika; tarirai, vachakurumidza kuuya vachichimbidzika.
\v 27 Hapana achaneta kana kugumburwa pakati pavo; hakuna achakotsira kana kuvata; bhanhire rezviuno zvavo haringasunungurwi, rukanda rweshangu dzavo harungadambuki.
\v 28 Miseve yavo inopinza, uta hwavo hwese hwakakungwa; mazondo amabhiza avo achaita somusara, namavhiri engoro dzavo sechamupupuri;
\v 29 kuomba kwavo kuchaita sokwehadzi yeshumba, vachavomba savana veshumba; zvirokwazvo vachavomba, vachabata mhuka yavo, ndokuenda nayo, hapana angairwira.
\v 30 Nezuva iro vachavaombera sokutinhira kwegungwa; kana munhu akatarira nyika, achaona rima nokutambudzika; chiedza chichasvibiswa namakore ayo.
